      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RHYNO'S GIRL (2) dropped out early but hit the line hard, charging into second and beaten 3.5 lengths win (22.77) at this track in Maiden. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Rates highly and will give a great sight. IRISH LAD (4) is a newcomer for the Jade Murray kennel. Start all important from the squeeze box. Market moves likely to signal ability but profiles strongly for this. LOLA'S CHOICE (3) turned in a plain performance last time when sixth at this track over 388m behind Chronic Fluffy (23.45) in a Maiden. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Likely to play a prominent role. HIGH DEGREES (6) is a Peter Mattress-trained newcomer by Jungle Deuce out of Rivello. Can sneak into the frame with the right run.",
